{"tid":339444,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"（捐血養支那人）血庫存量偏低 紅會籲捐","createTime":"2017-07-29T05:30:22.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-13T03:57:58.000Z","uid":29314,"like":0,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"ede2cd059436632314de489178924031451ea822","tid":339444,"uid":29314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-29T05:30:22.000Z","msg":"又黎叫廢青捐血la！！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n香港紅十字會輸血服務中心公佈，周五只有682人捐血，成功收集528袋血液。<br />\n<br />\n&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n中心表示，一包血可救助最少3名病人，尤其呼籲年滿16歲的青少年加入捐血行列"},{"pid":"e119915fd4f567ef578f634138cdce6ab5dd1877","tid":339444,"uid":29314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-29T06:10:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c894975506939fbb01779285e124d2973fe611a1","tid":339444,"uid":103325,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-29T07:21:07.000Z","msg":"捐&hellip;捐佢老母"},{"pid":"a96f5368b0ab76db48cce4adb77aeb6f991c8f8a","tid":339444,"uid":29314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-29T07:59:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/07.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6ec42609b150130058d4eac4e7ee6a50e1fa744f","tid":339444,"uid":27568,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-29T08:05:01.000Z","msg":"上次捐話我梅毒假陽性（即係無事）<br />\n掉q 左我包血<br />\n之後一直無去捐了"},{"pid":"7f284e0ce8b7af0b90ab1b5f42abee8dc1087549","tid":339444,"uid":71655,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-03T11:04:51.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"7d5436fdc0d1156ee88c5dbde424b12fe700e2b5","tid":339444,"uid":29314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-04T13:18:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1c79ad249e8974d57f5f3e66e80102b246dafc78","tid":339444,"uid":71655,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-13T02:19:54.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"150779437b5945e4c1cafc4076d9fe54e563fa42","tid":339444,"uid":53524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-13T02:21:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 到時邊位巴打無血用直接PM我啦"},{"pid":"0a30184a06b2633ca6305bafc049a38e0cc2bfbb","tid":339444,"uid":30169,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-13T03:57:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>血液不足事件，作為繼房屋、土地、器官、奶粉、學位之後，另一個資源被分薄的案例<br />\n咁耐以黎，聽到依句最哽耳：捐血救人。 <br />\n屌你老味，捐錢都可以救人啦，知唔知幾多人因為無錢買標靶藥而死? <br />\n又唔見話香港住宅不足，叫人捐樓比人住？<br />\n又唔見手持十幾層樓收租既人捐錢? <br />\n錢就係你既，血就係大家既，我屌你老母啦。<br />\n啲人無血就要我捐比佢，我無錢無樓無女無希望又邊個捐比我/幫下我？ <br />\n仲要比班既得利益者迫你讓座OT 無補水，俾血佢繼續黎剝削我 ?</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}